OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 4 Jul to Mon 13 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure will dominate across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales over the weekend,
OL,8,Fbringing dry and warm conditions with
OL,9,Fplenty of sunshine for most. Scotland
OL,10,Fand Northern Ireland will probably see
OL,11,Fmore cloud this weekend, with periods
OL,12,Fof rain mainly affecting western
OL,13,FScotland at times. Into the following
OL,14,Fworking week, high pressure remains
OL,15,Fslow moving over England and Wales,
OL,16,Fperhaps extending northwards to bring
OL,17,Fdrier and warmer weather to Scotland
OL,18,Fand Northern Ireland. Winds will be
OL,19,Flight to moderate for most, though
OL,20,Fstronger around northern hills and
OL,21,Fcoasts near low pressure systems.
OL,22,FTemperatures will rise through the
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fperiod, perhaps becoming very warm or
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fhot in places.
